                    <li><strong>Weekends:</strong> Use as "medication holidays" to prevent tolerance</li>
                    <li>This keeps your brain producing its own neurotransmitters</li>
                </ul>

                <p style="margin-top:15px;"><strong>Monitor for:</strong></p>
